# My Top 5 Prompts

## 1. Email Writer
"Write email. Tone professional. 100 words. Include subject line."

## 2. Simplifier
"Explain [topic] to a 10-year-old. No jargon."

## 3. Decision Maker
"Compare A vs B. Give pros, cons, recommendation."

## 4. Action Extractor
"From this text, extract tasks with owner and deadline."

## 5. LinkedIn Hook
"Write 5 hooks about [topic] under 10 words each."
